Summary: UFO? not seen by eye but on camera images only
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking photos of chem trails with my cell phone as I waited for my grandson to get out of school. I didn't see any objects until I uploaded my pictures to my computer. There are 3 images of an object which I cropped, magnified and adjusted exposure and the real curious image of an object between tree branches and semi-circular in shape, can't be artifact on my camera lense. Very strange! Would like to know what it is. Thank you.
